          <versionCode>81</versionCode>
          <actionDesc>Passed House without amendment</actionDesc>
          <updateDate>2017-01-03T14:23:16Z</updateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary has been expanded because action occurred on the measure.)</p> <p><strong>Ensuring VA Employee Accountability Act</strong></p> <p>(Sec. 2) This bill requires the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) to retain a copy of any reprimand or admonishment received by a VA employee in the employee's permanent record.</p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2017-01-03</actionDate>
